Practical – 6 AIM To implement an Android application demonstrating programming of menus and dialogs for user interaction.
PROBLEM STATEMENT Design and develop an Android application that uses an Options Menu with multiple menu items. On selecting a menu item, display an appropriate dialog to show
information or to confirm user action, and perform the required operation based on the user’s response.
